

functional:

acceptance criteria:

- debug output shall be sent with DebugMsg_Error() or DebugMsg_Warning()
-> what is not a warning or an error condition shall not be printed to debug port
-> use Syslog_Info() instead


formatting:

- variables shall carry their physical unit in its name. e.g. "_kPa"
- pointer names shall have a prefix "p", followed by a capital letter
- function Parameters start with capital letter

naming conventions

- functions prefixed with "show_" are expected to print information in human readable form (associated with cli)
